p: In the District Court of the 3rd Judicial District in and for the County of King Territory of Washington.
In the matter of Jimmy Jardine alias Russell Habeas Corpus}

And now comes the said prisoner by his Atty John E. Costello and says that he is at present unable to procure the services of an Atty for pay and that he is unable to pay necessary clerk fees upon the filing of this petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus and asks that the same be filed
by his Atty John E. Costello
Subscribed and sworn to before me
